Description
-----------

nitro-pyxis - Pyxis logging for Nitro

Source
------

https://github.com/bbc/nitro-pyxis

Build
-----

In Jenkins:

* https://jenkins.bbc.co.uk/job/nitro-pyxis/

In a BBC sandbox:

1. BUILD_NUMBER=<N> ./mk_tgz.sh
2. mbt -s rpmbuild

